# PEO Onboarding Portal
# Two enrollment models supported:
#
# Model A — API integration (preferred)
# PEO connects their HR system (PrismHR, Rippling, ADP) to saludcompartida.ai API.
# API key generated on onboarding completion.
# Real-time enrollment, zero manual work.
# Target: G&A Partners and PEOs with PrismHR/Rippling.
#
# Model B — CSV upload
# PEO uploads employee file from saludcompartida.ai portal.
# Processed in bulk, errors logged to enrollment_uploads table.
# Frequency: weekly or during open enrollment periods.
# Target: smaller PEOs without API-capable HR systems.
#
# Model C (manual, one-by-one) — NOT supported.
# Too operationally expensive at this stage.
